        "text": "=You are a customer support knowledge base writer. Based on the following customer question and the human agent's answer, generate a clean FAQ entry.\n\nCustomer Question: {{ $json.customer_message }}\nHuman Agent Answer: {{ $json.human_answer }}\n\nReturn ONLY a JSON object in this exact format, nothing else:\n{\"question\": \"clean version of the customer question\", \"answer\": \"preserve the full detail from the human agent's answer, including all alternatives, recommendations, and actionable suggestions — do not summarize or shorten\"}",
